and-relaunches-as-jetpack-crm\'>WPTavern: Zero BS CRM Rebrands and Relaunches as Jetpack CRM</a></li></ul></div>','no'),(4013,'_transient_timeout_hm_backdrop-2f5f804b6785c0ad69cfc3b26c00','1595499242','no'),(4014,'_transient_hm_backdrop-2f5f804b6785c0ad69cfc3b26c00','a:2:{s:8:\"callback\";s:38:\"\\HM\\BackUpWordPress\\run_schedule_async\";s:6:\"params\";a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"1585305660\";}}','no');
